<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="134" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="134">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="134">
Twenty-one species: 15 in central and southern mainland China (Fujian, Guangdong, Guangxi, Guizhou, Hubei, Hunan, Jiangxi, Sichuan, Chongqing, Yunnan, Zhejiang), one in north Vietnam, five in Taiwan and one extending to the Ryukyu islands (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 13" captionStartId="F13" captionText="Figure 13. Distribution of Bredia." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.127.36608.figure13" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/318135" pageId="13" pageNumber="134" tableDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.127.36608.figure13">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
